=======================================================================

%^RED%^%^BOLD%^ SYNTAX :: %^RESET%^ set_smell ( target, message )
%^RED%^%^BOLD%^ SYNTAX :: %^RESET%^ set_smell ( target, function )

This function is present in all objects. It will add the smell named
in the string target into the object. Either a string message can be
defined or a function pointer (: :) .

see also ::

set_smells, remove_smell, remove_smells, query_smell, query_smells

